{"results":[{"aya":"127","id":3059,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"我不为传达命令而向你们索取任何报酬；我的报酬，只由全世界的主负担。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"128","id":3060,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"你们在高地上建筑一个纪念物，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"129","id":3061,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"以供游戏。你们设立一些堡垒，好象你们将永居尘世一样。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"130","id":3062,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"你们惩治（他人）的时候，你们是很残酷的。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"131","id":3063,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"你们应当敬畏真主之名，应当服从我。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"132","id":3064,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"你们应当敬畏主，他以你们所知道的赏赐你们，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"133","id":3065,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"他赏赐你们牲畜和子嗣，","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":33,"previousPage":"/zh/s026-18.json","nextPage":"/zh/s026-20.json"}}